{{Infobox University |image_name = |image_size = 200px |name = Center for Strategic Studies - Jordan |native_name = مركز الدراسات الاستراتيجية |motto = |mottoeng = |established = 1998 |type = Political and economical Research Center |calendar= |endowment = |chairman = |director = Musa Shteiwi |students = |undergrad = |postgrad= |faculty = |staff = |city = [[Amman]] |country = [[Jordan]] |campus = [[University of Jordan]] main campus |website = http://www.jcss.org |logo = }}
The '''Center for Strategic Studies Jordan (CSS)''' was established in 1998 with the objective of providing government bodies and organizations in the public and private sectors with high-impact studies of politics, foreign policy, economy and society of countries in the [[Middle East]] region. The center also performs high accuracy polls.<ref>[http://www.jcss.org CSS website]</ref>
