'''Fujian Agriculture and Forestry University''' ({{zh|s=福建农林大学}}) is a public university in Jinshan, [[Fuzhou]], [[Fujian]], China.

Fujian Agriculture and Forestry University's library collection contains more than 1.63 million volumes.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.lib.fjau.edu.cn/FJAULIB/situation.html |script-title=zh:全馆概况 |accessdate=2007-12-09 |publisher=福建农林大学图书馆 |language=zh |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071121141414/http://www.lib.fjau.edu.cn/FJAULIB/situation.html |archivedate=2007-11-21 |df= }}</ref>

==History==
The university was founded in 1936. It is now known as the Fujian Agriculture and Forestry University is public university focused on the development of agriculture and forestry.

